# Title: Enabled User Right in AD to Control User Objects
# Author: @neu5ron
# Date: 2017-07-30
# Level: high
# Description: Detects scenario where if a user is assigned the SeEnableDelegationPrivilege right in Active Directory it would allow control of other AD user objects.
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.persistence, attack.t1098
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_alert_active_directory_user_control.yml

EventID=4704 PrivilegeList="*SeEnableDelegationPrivilege*"